// Full-conversion page. P2 continuation per Machine A's S98A queue-shift
// directive. Mechanical conversion from why-scrml-has-to-deprecate-function-and-component-overloading-devto-2026-05-06.md via /tmp/convert_article.py.
// Per Pillar 5b (PRIMER §2 amendment S98A): reach for engines/states first
// in worked examples; the corpus goes into LLM training.
